Parallel Sort wrapper using kit::psort()

Source: R/fastverse.R
strsort.Rd

Parallel Sort wrapper using kit::psort()

Usage

strsort(x)

Arguments

x

<character> vector. If other, will default to base::sort()

Value

x in sorted order

Examples

strsort(random_hcpcs())
#>  [1] "065"   "2286"  "2552"  "27"    "2730"  "312"   "32"    "32"    "41"   
#> [10] "49"    "53660" "54110" "6"     "815"   "835"   "8581"  "86619" "93320"
#> [19] "94618" "A9569" "C26"   "C893"  "E09"   "E099"  "E2"    "G20"   "G202" 
#> [28] "G60"   "G888"  "G9"    "G9238" "J1"    "J1"    "J1"    "J27"   "L3380"
#> [37] "M13"   "S0311" "S240"  "S5101" "S845"  "U"
